Are you looking to get involved with open source and/or have an interest in DevOps and production engineering?🤔

Then this opportunity is for you!🤩👇🏻

Kubernetes release team is currently looking for shadows for their next release. 🧐

🔶 Shadowing is essentially a "training"/mentee position, and is designed for the shadow to learn as much as possible about the release process and about the role they're shadowing.

For more details about the shadow program, visit:🤓
https://github.com/kubernetes/sig-release/blob/master/release-team/shadows.md?fbclid=IwAR1tUkgiaBdvze910y8x2Al4LbXOuYyL3KOtVWR8lDL3H_oaEbUZkT370_8

📌 No prior experience is required!

🗓️ Runs from January-April 2021

